---
title: Fajita-Style Chicken Bowl with Basmati Rice and Lime Crema
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour, this dish gives you the fiesta without the fuss! Bell peppers and green onions pair perfectly with tender chicken for a fun fajita bowl that comes together with our fabulous Mexican seasoning.
